title: Bach, JS - The Keyboard Concertos - Perahia, ASMF
description:
Bach, JS: The Keyboard Concertos.

This sublime collection sees Murray Perahia conduct (from the piano) the Academy of St Martin in the Fields through Bach's solo Keyboard Concertos.

The contents of the three discs are as follows:

DISC I
Keyboard Concertos Nos. 1, 2, and 4.

DISC II
Keyboard Concertos Nos. 3, 5, 6, and 7.

DISC III
Concerto for Flute, Violin, and Harpsichord in A minor, Brandenburg Concerto No. 5 in D major, and Italian Concerto in F major.

The recordings were made by Sony between 2000 and 2003, and this compilation was released in 2011.

Please enjoy.
